ost popular male names. This popularity was reinforced when  George I  came to the throne in  1714 , bringing this name with him from Germany. It has been one of the most popular English boys' names ever since."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"George Solers was born from 1175 to 1195 as the son of William Solers. He had at least 1 son."},"et":{"between 1175 and 1195–":"1175 kuni 1195–Surnud","1175–Male":"1175–Surnud","1215–Male":"1215–Surnud","1155–Male":"1155–Surnud","1215":"1215","1155":"1155","1175":"1175","between 1175 and 1195":"1175 kuni 1195"},"fi":{"between 1175 and 1195–":"vuodesta 1175 vuoteen 1195–Kuollut","1175–Male":"1175–Kuollut","1215–Male":"1215–Kuollut","1155–Male":"1155–Kuollut","1215":"1215","1155":"1155","1175":"1175","between 1175 and 1195":"vuodesta 1175 vuoteen 1195"},"fr":{"between 1175 and 1195–":"du 1175 au 1195–Décédé","1175–Male":"1175–Décédé","1215–Male":"1215–Décédé","1155–Male":"1155–Décédé","1215":"1215","1155":"1155","1175":"1175","between 1175 and 1195":"du 1175 au 1195","lifeSummary":"George Solers est né du 1175 au 1195, fils de William Solers. Il a eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"between 1175 and 1195–":"von 1175 bis 1195–Verstorben","1175–Male":"1175–Verstorben","1215–Male":"1215–Verstorben","1155–Male":"1155–Verstorben","1215":"1215","1155":"1155","1175":"1175","between 1175 and 1195":"von 1175 bis 1195","lifeSummary":"George Solers wurde von 1175 bis 1195, als Sohn von William Solers geboren. Er hatte mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"between 1175 and 1195–":"from 1175 to 1195–Desede","1175–Male":"1175–Desede","1215–Male":"1215–Desede","1155–Male":"1155–Desede","1215":"1215","1155":"1155","1175":"1175","between 1175 and 1195":"from 1175 to 1195"},"hu":{"between 1175 and 1195–":"között 1175 to 1195–elhunyt","1175–Male":"1175–elhunyt","1215–Male":"1215–elhunyt","1155–Male":"1155–elhunyt","1215":"1215","1155":"1155","1175":"1175","between 1175 and 1195":"között 1175 to 1195"},"id":{"between 1175 and 1195–":"dari 1175 hingga 1195–Telah Men